Package: coastalNet
Title: Facilitating Oceanographic Connectivity Analysis
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jorge", "Assis", , "jorgemfa@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6624-4820"))
Description: 'coastalNet' provides tools to access, analyze, and visualize estimates of oceanographic connectivity driven by ocean currents. It simplifies the exploration of how currents influence marine biodiversity patterns, including dispersal, population structure, and species resilience. 
